title: No 10 year gift.
body: Hey i just wanted to let someone know i didnt get my 10 year gift/icon and idk where to post this so hopefully this is the right place.

replies.body: Gifts are not doing being sent out.  There's a lot of accounts to gift so it will take some time, but you can stay up to date through our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight!
